{"tid":1715836,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環OL泳鏡上陣迎防暴","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T08:07:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ae4b1e1424e20724ae387c81f0e7ff64596c7713","tid":1715836,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:41:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191113/HGVQPNFUCVAXLLPLPHGH7L62AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FHGVQPNFUCVAXLLPLPHGH7L62AE%2F&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=58328533\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FHGVQPNFUCVAXLLPLPHGH7L62AE%2F&h=fc8a06a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191113/HGVQPNFUCVAXLLPLPHGH7L62AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n中環OL泳鏡上陣迎防暴<br />\n<br />\n【白領反抗】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港金融核心區域中環連續兩日上演怒火街頭，過千名OL、西裝白領勇敢走到街頭「和你Lunch」，他們佔據干諾道中等重要幹道，除了在衝衝子後方作強大後盾，亦有OL勇於在前線傘陣中，戴上泳鏡迎接警方推進。面對特首林鄭月娥揚言破壞香港的「暴徒」不會得逞，有中環人揚言「我哋都唔會畀林鄭得逞！」警方則繼續武力鎮壓，包括施放多輪催淚彈，更命令被制服的市民儼如戰俘般舉手投降。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰李詠希 黃翠儀 張雅婷<br />\n<br />\n午飯時間，中環人放棄「搵食」，與香港人站在同一陣線。逾千名上班族在黑衣人帶領下築起路障，在街頭快閃。他們逼爆畢打街、德輔道中和干諾道中，人潮更延伸至皇后大道中，沿路呼喊「Fight for freedom, stand with Hong Kong」等反修例口號，並高舉代表五大訴求的「五」字手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191113/large/1573579143_6e66.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573579143_6e66.gif&h=c541e1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】有穿西裙、平底鞋、戴泳鏡和口罩的OL在傘陣後方半蹲備戰。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191113/large/1573579140_2cd4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573579140_2cd4.gif&h=dbcde020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】防暴警推進，並以防暴槍驅散。董立華攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191113/large/1573579141_c51b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573579141_c51b.gif&h=a0ed3336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】恤衫友與OL化作衝衝子後盾，連成一線傳遞磚塊。許頌明攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191113/large/1573579142_f410.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573579142_f410.gif&h=94b16c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】警方迫令被制服的市民儼如戰俘般舉手投降。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逼舉手 警視市民如戰俘<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：學生徵物資 一呼百應<br />\n<br />\n當防暴警員出現時，中環人不再和理非，有穿西裙、平底鞋、戴泳鏡和口罩的OL在傘陣後方半蹲着備戰，隨時面對警方推進；亦有西裝男高舉用英文撰寫的字句︰「恭喜警察，你們終於可以踏足大學及在中環工作」。<br />\n<br />\n從事酒店業的吳先生昨日罷工，參與快閃堵路，表達對警方濫捕的不滿，「運動已經過咗成五個月，政府仲未滿足五大訴求。喺呢五個月之中，越多人被捕，越多人行出嚟，包括我。」他又指，在中環快閃可令商業活動停頓和交通工具停駛，冀向林鄭集氣反抗，「我哋唔會畀林鄭得逞！」<br />\n<br />\n從事餐飲業、帶同「光復香港 時代革命」旗幟到場阿Cat說，自己任職的酒吧人手不足，難以罷工，但會全力支持，因此趕在開工前來聲援。她說︰「好似中環呢班白領係香港比較重要嘅一群，嚟到第五個月，佢哋終於肯喺lunch time行出嚟，係和理非嘅升級」。對於特首林鄭月娥稱「暴徒唔會得逞」，她斥：「佢講嘅嘢你都好信嘅？總之我哋繼續堅持自己」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191113/large/1573579142_0b98.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573579142_0b98.gif&h=d88d34fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑衣人現身時，一眾中環人舉手相迎。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191113/large/1573579143_0e6b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573579143_0e6b.gif&h=fc98d6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西裝男以英文紙牌嘲警察終可踏足大學及在中環工作。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n防暴警員與中環人一直對峙逾兩小時，其間有警員開咪警告眾人離開，舉藍旗和黑旗，甚至有警員舉槍指嚇市民。不過，中環人未有膽怯，反而則大叫警方「收隊」，人數之多一度迫令警員撤退。<br />\n<br />\n下午3時15分，快閃行動結束，防暴警突然沿畢打街推進，有警員發射催淚彈驅散及使用防暴槍，其後制服十多人，逐一檢查他們的隨身物品，在等候期間，所有被制服的人都被迫如戰俘般舉起雙手。防暴警員之後沿畢打街後退，但有市民上前向警員高叫「殺人犯」，警員隨即在畢打街天橋向地面人群連環施放多枚催淚彈，人群爭相走避，一名男子疑被催淚彈打中頭部流血，衣服和地面均有血迹，需由義務急救員治理和包紮。現場遺下多枚催淚彈殼，包括一枚未有爆裂的手擲催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n入夜後，中環怒火繼續，百名示威者佔據中環畢打街一帶，超過50名防暴警員及速龍小隊到場，邊舉藍旗邊向康樂廣場行人天橋及畢打街發射多枚胡椒球彈。於皇后大道中及畢打街交界，至少五人被制服帶上警車。大批圍觀市民指罵警察是「黑社會」、「殺人犯」等，在場警員反斥市民是「曱甴」。民主黨立法會議員許智峯到場調停。"},{"pid":"558643c0c8d4cab542a21f8ee050b7749381240c","tid":1715836,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645a1187b3ac882c483c796a47646225c17c75fa","tid":1715836,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435ff0594ff2463fa59da1ff1654e62bee463bd3","tid":1715836,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:46:07.000Z","msg":"各位OL買靚衫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n換季啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c022977f1459eef415e54a00395572015fb720","tid":1715836,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次唔好著裙"},{"pid":"2b8554c7e25335e25c8ac15035edad62a7355c63","tid":1715836,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e932db57858d58b47b3867835f02afd4c45f3fa6","tid":1715836,"uid":229296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於由傳水-&gt;傳遮-&gt;到傳磚<br />\n回想返612起磚都仲比人屌係鬼，<br />\n到而家香港人終於打開左個心理關口<br />\n但用左5個月，死傷左幾多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec1e8ff2ee6fc20c6fb8b9506f8ef294a7fa266","tid":1715836,"uid":48604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"咁正比黑警捉到實渣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac13946ad8cca8e295cb57fb926b1768d1f2d2c6","tid":1715836,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b63d21b5a59705e2c32593b7c7360b32848c8a","tid":1715836,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:54:49.000Z","msg":"終於進化到磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0863336dbf91ced28a04d2ea47ecfbcae471b14","tid":1715836,"uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/lkpu1RTwzVsgiBoRuc54H5UFgHI=/802x561/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/I74NZGJT3P4VBXDZZVSQORUZ4A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Flkpu1RTwzVsgiBoRuc54H5UFgHI%3D%2F802x561%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FI74NZGJT3P4VBXDZZVSQORUZ4A.gif&h=f8ebb13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】有穿西裙、平底鞋、戴泳鏡和口罩的OL在傘陣後方半蹲備戰。<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"f28206e0d5ea157c844522fc3fdf172bd4893460","tid":1715836,"uid":269929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0863336dbf91ced28a04d2ea47ecfbcae471b14","tid":1715836,"uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/lkpu1RTwzVsgiBoRuc54H5UFgHI=/802x561/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/I74NZGJT3P4VBXDZZVSQORUZ4A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Flkpu1RTwzVsgiBoRuc54H5UFgHI%3D%2F802x561%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FI74NZGJT3P4VBXDZZVSQORUZ4A.gif&h=f8ebb13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】有穿西裙、平底鞋、戴泳鏡和口罩的OL在傘陣後方半蹲備戰。<br />\nAppleDaily"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}